    "Table 5 summarizes the key obligations for each category of intermediary service under the DSA's graduated regulatory approach.",
    "Key mechanisms and provisionsThe DSA establishes several mechanisms and provisions constituting core pillars of its regulatory approach.",
    "As Table 6 summarizes, the core mechanisms instituted under the DSA tie to specific articles and recitals which elaborate their objectives and requirements.",
    "For instance, Notice-and-takedown procedures (Art.",
    "14,16,17) The DSA provides a harmonized notice-and-action framework for reporting and removing illegal online content across the EU."
